  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, as a bonus action you can awaken the slumbering demon inside of you. For 1 minute, you emit a 5-foot aura dark malevolent chakra, gain a +1 bonus to AC, and a number of times equal to half your proficiency bonus per activation of this form, when you take the attack action, you can replace one or more attacks with a Genjutsu of C-Rank or lower. The Genjutsu must require an attack roll, and cannot have CS or NT components or a range of self. You can activate this transformation once per long rest.</p>",
